  "title": "Machine Operator",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></h3><ul><li>Fabricate parts to meet customer's requirements/standards as per their drawings.</li><li>Run production according to production schedules and output targets.</li><li>Ensure that parts fabricated meet delivery schedules.</li><li>Perform regular cleaning and maintenance of the machines and equipment.</li><li>Perform 5S and cleaning of the work area on a daily basis.</li><li>Contribute to quality and output improvement efforts.</li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements:</strong></h3><ul><li>Nitec of Higher Nitec in precision machining is preferred.</li><li>Ability to understand engineering drawings and technical instructions.</li><li>Knowledge of using measurement instruments to verify part dimensions.</li><li>Willing to work on rotating shifts,</li><li>Possess good attitude and teamwork.</li></ul>",
